                              <bibl>
                                    <title type="article" key="#ChicagoDailyTribune1902">To Explore
                                          the Strange Island of San Nicolas: An Expedition from the
                                          University of California Will Visit the Gruesome Land That
                                          is Spread Over with Skulls and Thighbones of a Lost
                                          Race.</title>
